{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 1", "sort_key": "0001", "text_original": "《曲禮》曰：「毋不敬，儼若思，安定辭。」安民哉！", "text_normalized": "《曲禮》曰：「毋不敬，儼若思，安定辭。」安民哉！", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 2", "sort_key": "0002", "text_original": "敖不可長，欲不可從，志不可滿，樂不可極。", "text_normalized": "敖不可長，欲不可從，志不可滿，樂不可極。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 3", "sort_key": "0003", "text_original": "賢者狎而敬之，畏而愛之。愛而知其惡，憎而知其善。積而能散，安安而能遷。臨財毋茍得，臨難毋茍免。很毋求勝，分毋求多。疑事毋質，直而勿有。", "text_normalized": "賢者狎而敬之，畏而愛之。愛而知其惡，憎而知其善。積而能散，安安而能遷。臨財毋茍得，臨難毋茍免。很毋求勝，分毋求多。疑事毋質，直而勿有。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 4", "sort_key": "0004", "text_original": "若夫，坐如尸，立如齊。", "text_normalized": "若夫，坐如尸，立如齊。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 5", "sort_key": "0005", "text_original": "禮從宜，使從俗。", "text_normalized": "禮從宜，使從俗。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 6", "sort_key": "0006", "text_original": "夫禮者所以定親疏，決嫌疑，別同異，明是非也。", "text_normalized": "夫禮者所以定親疏，決嫌疑，別同異，明是非也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 7", "sort_key": "0007", "text_original": "禮，不妄說人，不辭費。禮，不逾節，不侵侮，不好狎。修身踐言，謂之善行。行修言道，禮之質也。禮聞取於人，不聞取人。禮聞來學，不聞往教。", "text_normalized": "禮，不妄說人，不辭費。禮，不逾節，不侵侮，不好狎。修身踐言，謂之善行。行修言道，禮之質也。禮聞取於人，不聞取人。禮聞來學，不聞往教。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 8", "sort_key": "0008", "text_original": "道德仁義，非禮不成，教訓正俗，非禮不備。分爭辨訟，非禮不決。君臣上下父子兄弟，非禮不定。宦學事師，非禮不親。班朝治軍，蒞官行法，非禮威嚴不行。禱祠祭祀，供給鬼神，非禮不誠不莊。是以君子恭敬撙節退讓以明禮。", "text_normalized": "道德仁義，非禮不成，教訓正俗，非禮不備。分爭辨訟，非禮不決。君臣上下父子兄弟，非禮不定。宦學事師，非禮不親。班朝治軍，蒞官行法，非禮威嚴不行。禱祠祭祀，供給鬼神，非禮不誠不莊。是以君子恭敬撙節退讓以明禮。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 9", "sort_key": "0009", "text_original": "鸚鵡能言，不離飛鳥；猩猩能言，不離禽獸。今人而無禮，雖能言，不亦禽獸之心乎？夫唯禽獸無禮，故父子聚麀。是故聖人作，為禮以教人。使人以有禮，知自別於禽獸。", "text_normalized": "鸚鵡能言，不離飛鳥；猩猩能言，不離禽獸。今人而無禮，雖能言，不亦禽獸之心乎？夫唯禽獸無禮，故父子聚麀。是故聖人作，為禮以教人。使人以有禮，知自別於禽獸。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 10", "sort_key": "0010", "text_original": "太上貴德，其次務施報。禮尚往來。往而不來，非禮也；來而不往，亦非禮也。人有禮則安，無禮則危。故曰：禮者不可不學也。", "text_normalized": "太上貴德，其次務施報。禮尚往來。往而不來，非禮也；來而不往，亦非禮也。人有禮則安，無禮則危。故曰：禮者不可不學也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 11", "sort_key": "0011", "text_original": "夫禮者，自卑而尊人。雖負販者，必有尊也，而況富貴乎？富貴而知好禮，則不驕不淫；貧賤而知好禮，則志不懾。", "text_normalized": "夫禮者，自卑而尊人。雖負販者，必有尊也，而況富貴乎？富貴而知好禮，則不驕不淫；貧賤而知好禮，則志不懾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 12", "sort_key": "0012", "text_original": "人生十年曰幼，學。二十曰弱，冠。三十曰壯，有室。四十曰強，而仕。五十曰艾，服官政。六十曰耆，指使。七十曰老，而傳。八十、九十曰耄，七年曰悼，悼與耄雖有罪，不加刑焉。百年曰期，頤。", "text_normalized": "人生十年曰幼，學。二十曰弱，冠。三十曰壯，有室。四十曰強，而仕。五十曰艾，服官政。六十曰耆，指使。七十曰老，而傳。八十、九十曰耄，七年曰悼，悼與耄雖有罪，不加刑焉。百年曰期，頤。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 13", "sort_key": "0013", "text_original": "大夫七十而致事。若不得謝，則必賜之几杖，行役以婦人。適四方，乘安車。自稱曰老夫，於其國則稱名；越國而問焉，必告之以其制。", "text_normalized": "大夫七十而致事。若不得謝，則必賜之几杖，行役以婦人。適四方，乘安車。自稱曰老夫，於其國則稱名；越國而問焉，必告之以其制。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 14", "sort_key": "0014", "text_original": "謀於長者，必操几杖以從之。長者問，不辭讓而對，非禮也。", "text_normalized": "謀於長者，必操几杖以從之。長者問，不辭讓而對，非禮也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 15", "sort_key": "0015", "text_original": "凡為人子之禮：冬溫而夏凊，昏定而晨省，在醜夷不爭。", "text_normalized": "凡為人子之禮：冬溫而夏凊，昏定而晨省，在醜夷不爭。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 16", "sort_key": "0016", "text_original": "夫為人子者，三賜不及車馬。故州閭鄉黨稱其孝也，兄弟親戚稱其慈也，僚友稱其弟也，執友稱其仁也，交游稱其信也。見父之執，不謂之進不敢進，不謂之退不敢退，不問不敢對。此孝子之行也。", "text_normalized": "夫為人子者，三賜不及車馬。故州閭鄉黨稱其孝也，兄弟親戚稱其慈也，僚友稱其弟也，執友稱其仁也，交游稱其信也。見父之執，不謂之進不敢進，不謂之退不敢退，不問不敢對。此孝子之行也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 17", "sort_key": "0017", "text_original": "夫為人子者：出必告，反必面，所游必有常，所習必有業。恒言不稱老。年長以倍則父事之，十年以長則兄事之，五年以長則肩隨之。群居五人，則長者必異席。", "text_normalized": "夫為人子者：出必告，反必面，所游必有常，所習必有業。恒言不稱老。年長以倍則父事之，十年以長則兄事之，五年以長則肩隨之。群居五人，則長者必異席。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 18", "sort_key": "0018", "text_original": "為人子者，居不主奧，坐不中席，行不中道，立不中門。食饗不為概，祭祀不為尸。聽於無聲，視於無形。不登高，不臨深。不茍訾，不茍笑。", "text_normalized": "為人子者，居不主奧，坐不中席，行不中道，立不中門。食饗不為概，祭祀不為尸。聽於無聲，視於無形。不登高，不臨深。不茍訾，不茍笑。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 19", "sort_key": "0019", "text_original": "孝子不服暗，不登危，懼辱親也。父母存，不許友以死。不有私財。", "text_normalized": "孝子不服暗，不登危，懼辱親也。父母存，不許友以死。不有私財。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 20", "sort_key": "0020", "text_original": "為人子者：父母存，冠衣不純素。孤子當室，冠衣不純采。", "text_normalized": "為人子者：父母存，冠衣不純素。孤子當室，冠衣不純采。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 21", "sort_key": "0021", "text_original": "幼子常視毋誑，童子不衣裘裳。立必正方。不傾聽。長者與之提攜，則兩手奉長者之手。負劍辟咡詔之，則掩口而對。", "text_normalized": "幼子常視毋誑，童子不衣裘裳。立必正方。不傾聽。長者與之提攜，則兩手奉長者之手。負劍辟咡詔之，則掩口而對。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 22", "sort_key": "0022", "text_original": "從於先生，不越路而與人言。遭先生於道，趨而進，正立拱手。先生與之言則對；不與之言則趨而退。", "text_normalized": "從於先生，不越路而與人言。遭先生於道，趨而進，正立拱手。先生與之言則對；不與之言則趨而退。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 23", "sort_key": "0023", "text_original": "從長者而上丘陵，則必鄉長者所視。", "text_normalized": "從長者而上丘陵，則必鄉長者所視。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 24", "sort_key": "0024", "text_original": "登城不指，城上不呼。", "text_normalized": "登城不指，城上不呼。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 25", "sort_key": "0025", "text_original": "將適舍，求毋固。將上堂，聲必揚。戶外有二屨，言聞則入，言不聞則不入。將入戶，視必下。入戶奉扃，視瞻毋回；戶開亦開，戶闔亦闔；有後入者，闔而勿遂。毋踐屨，毋踖席，摳衣趨隅。必慎唯諾。", "text_normalized": "將適舍，求毋固。將上堂，聲必揚。戶外有二屨，言聞則入，言不聞則不入。將入戶，視必下。入戶奉扃，視瞻毋回；戶開亦開，戶闔亦闔；有後入者，闔而勿遂。毋踐屨，毋踖席，摳衣趨隅。必慎唯諾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 26", "sort_key": "0026", "text_original": "大夫士出入君門，由闑右，不踐閾。", "text_normalized": "大夫士出入君門，由闑右，不踐閾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 27", "sort_key": "0027", "text_original": "凡與客入者，每門讓於客。客至於寢門，則主人請入為席，然後出迎客。客固辭，主人肅客而入。主人入門而右，客入門而左。主人就東階，客就西階，客若降等，則就主人之階。主人固辭，然後客復就西階。主人與客讓登，主人先登，客從之，拾級聚足，連步以上。上於東階則先右足，上於西階則先左足。", "text_normalized": "凡與客入者，每門讓於客。客至於寢門，則主人請入為席，然後出迎客。客固辭，主人肅客而入。主人入門而右，客入門而左。主人就東階，客就西階，客若降等，則就主人之階。主人固辭，然後客復就西階。主人與客讓登，主人先登，客從之，拾級聚足，連步以上。上於東階則先右足，上於西階則先左足。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 28", "sort_key": "0028", "text_original": "帷薄之外不趨，堂上不趨，執玉不趨。堂上接武，堂下布武。室中不翔，并坐不橫肱。授立不跪，授坐不立。", "text_normalized": "帷薄之外不趨，堂上不趨，執玉不趨。堂上接武，堂下布武。室中不翔，并坐不橫肱。授立不跪，授坐不立。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 29", "sort_key": "0029", "text_original": "凡為長者糞之禮，必加帚於箕上，以袂拘而退；其塵不及長者，以箕自鄉而扱之。奉席如橋衡，請席何鄉，請衽何趾。席：南鄉北鄉，以西方為上；東鄉西鄉，以南方為上。", "text_normalized": "凡為長者糞之禮，必加帚於箕上，以袂拘而退；其塵不及長者，以箕自鄉而扱之。奉席如橋衡，請席何鄉，請衽何趾。席：南鄉北鄉，以西方為上；東鄉西鄉，以南方為上。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 30", "sort_key": "0030", "text_original": "若非飲食之客，則布席，席間函丈。主人跪正席，客跪撫席而辭。客徹重席，主人固辭。客踐席，乃坐。主人不問，客不先舉。", "text_normalized": "若非飲食之客，則布席，席間函丈。主人跪正席，客跪撫席而辭。客徹重席，主人固辭。客踐席，乃坐。主人不問，客不先舉。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 31", "sort_key": "0031", "text_original": "將即席，容毋怍。兩手摳衣去齊尺。衣毋撥，足毋蹶。先生書策琴瑟在前，坐而遷之，戒勿越。虛坐盡後，食坐盡前。坐必安，執爾顏。長者不及，毋儳言。正爾容，聽必恭。毋剿說，毋雷同。必則古昔，稱先王。", "text_normalized": "將即席，容毋怍。兩手摳衣去齊尺。衣毋撥，足毋蹶。先生書策琴瑟在前，坐而遷之，戒勿越。虛坐盡後，食坐盡前。坐必安，執爾顏。長者不及，毋儳言。正爾容，聽必恭。毋剿說，毋雷同。必則古昔，稱先王。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 32", "sort_key": "0032", "text_original": "侍坐於先生：先生問焉，終則對。請業則起，請益則起。父召無諾，先生召無諾，唯而起。", "text_normalized": "侍坐於先生：先生問焉，終則對。請業則起，請益則起。父召無諾，先生召無諾，唯而起。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 33, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 33", "sort_key": "0033", "text_original": "侍坐於所尊敬，毋餘席。見同等不起。燭至起，食至起，上客起。燭不見跋。尊客之前不叱狗。讓食不唾。", "text_normalized": "侍坐於所尊敬，毋餘席。見同等不起。燭至起，食至起，上客起。燭不見跋。尊客之前不叱狗。讓食不唾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 34, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 34", "sort_key": "0034", "text_original": "侍坐於君子，君子欠伸，撰杖屨，視日蚤莫，侍坐者請出矣。侍坐於君子，君子問更端，則起而對。侍坐於君子，若有告者曰：「少間」，愿有復也；則左右屏而待。", "text_normalized": "侍坐於君子，君子欠伸，撰杖屨，視日蚤莫，侍坐者請出矣。侍坐於君子，君子問更端，則起而對。侍坐於君子，若有告者曰：「少間」，愿有復也；則左右屏而待。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 35, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 35", "sort_key": "0035", "text_original": "毋側聽，毋噭應，毋淫視，毋怠荒。游毋倨，立毋跛，坐毋箕，寢毋伏。斂髮毋髢，冠毋免，勞毋袒，暑毋褰裳。", "text_normalized": "毋側聽，毋噭應，毋淫視，毋怠荒。游毋倨，立毋跛，坐毋箕，寢毋伏。斂髮毋髢，冠毋免，勞毋袒，暑毋褰裳。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 36, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 36", "sort_key": "0036", "text_original": "侍坐於長者，屨不上於堂，解屨不敢當階。就屨，跪而舉之，屏於側。鄉長者而屨；跪而遷屨，俯而納屨。", "text_normalized": "侍坐於長者，屨不上於堂，解屨不敢當階。就屨，跪而舉之，屏於側。鄉長者而屨；跪而遷屨，俯而納屨。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 37, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 37", "sort_key": "0037", "text_original": "離坐離立，毋往參焉；離立者，不出中間。", "text_normalized": "離坐離立，毋往參焉；離立者，不出中間。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 38, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 38", "sort_key": "0038", "text_original": "男女不雜坐，不同椸枷，不同巾櫛，不親授。嫂叔不通問，諸母不漱裳。外言不入於梱，內言不出於捆。", "text_normalized": "男女不雜坐，不同椸枷，不同巾櫛，不親授。嫂叔不通問，諸母不漱裳。外言不入於梱，內言不出於捆。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 39, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 39", "sort_key": "0039", "text_original": "女子許嫁，纓；非有大故，不入其門。姑姊妹女子子，已嫁而反，兄弟弗與同席而坐，弗與同器而食。父子不同席。", "text_normalized": "女子許嫁，纓；非有大故，不入其門。姑姊妹女子子，已嫁而反，兄弟弗與同席而坐，弗與同器而食。父子不同席。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 40, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 40", "sort_key": "0040", "text_original": "男女非有行媒，不相知名；非受幣，不交不親。故日月以告君，齊戒以告鬼神，為酒食以召鄉黨僚友，以厚其別也。", "text_normalized": "男女非有行媒，不相知名；非受幣，不交不親。故日月以告君，齊戒以告鬼神，為酒食以召鄉黨僚友，以厚其別也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 41, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 41", "sort_key": "0041", "text_original": "取妻不取同姓；故買妾不知其姓則卜之。寡婦之子，非有見焉，弗與為友。", "text_normalized": "取妻不取同姓；故買妾不知其姓則卜之。寡婦之子，非有見焉，弗與為友。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 42, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 42", "sort_key": "0042", "text_original": "賀取妻者，曰：「某子使某聞子有客，使某羞。」", "text_normalized": "賀取妻者，曰：「某子使某聞子有客，使某羞。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 43, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 43", "sort_key": "0043", "text_original": "貧者不以貨財為禮，老者不以筋力為禮。", "text_normalized": "貧者不以貨財為禮，老者不以筋力為禮。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 44, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 44", "sort_key": "0044", "text_original": "名子者不以國，不以日月，不以隱疾，不以山川。男女異長。男子二十，冠而字。父前，子名；君前，臣名。女子許嫁，笄而字。", "text_normalized": "名子者不以國，不以日月，不以隱疾，不以山川。男女異長。男子二十，冠而字。父前，子名；君前，臣名。女子許嫁，笄而字。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 45, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 45", "sort_key": "0045", "text_original": "凡進食之禮，左殽右胾，食居人之左，羹居人之右。膾炙處外，醯醬處內，蔥渫處末，酒漿處右。以脯修置者，左朐右末。", "text_normalized": "凡進食之禮，左殽右胾，食居人之左，羹居人之右。膾炙處外，醯醬處內，蔥渫處末，酒漿處右。以脯修置者，左朐右末。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 46, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 46", "sort_key": "0046", "text_original": "客若降等執食興辭，主人興辭於客，然後客坐。主人延客祭：祭食，祭所先進。殽之序，遍祭之。三飯，主人延客食胾，然後辯殽。主人未辯，客不虛口。", "text_normalized": "客若降等執食興辭，主人興辭於客，然後客坐。主人延客祭：祭食，祭所先進。殽之序，遍祭之。三飯，主人延客食胾，然後辯殽。主人未辯，客不虛口。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 47, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 47", "sort_key": "0047", "text_original": "侍食於長者，主人親饋，則拜而食；主人不親饋，則不拜而食。共食不飽，共飯不澤手。", "text_normalized": "侍食於長者，主人親饋，則拜而食；主人不親饋，則不拜而食。共食不飽，共飯不澤手。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 48, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 48", "sort_key": "0048", "text_original": "毋摶飯，毋放飯，毋流歠，毋吒食，毋嚙骨，毋反魚肉，毋投與狗骨。毋固獲，毋揚飯。飯黍毋以箸。毋嚃羹，毋絮羹，毋刺齒，毋歠醢。客絮羹，主人辭不能亨。客歠醢，主人辭以窶。濡肉齒決，乾肉不齒決。毋嘬炙。卒食，客自前跪，徹飯齊以授相者，主人興辭於客，然後客坐。", "text_normalized": "毋摶飯，毋放飯，毋流歠，毋吒食，毋嚙骨，毋反魚肉，毋投與狗骨。毋固獲，毋揚飯。飯黍毋以箸。毋嚃羹，毋絮羹，毋刺齒，毋歠醢。客絮羹，主人辭不能亨。客歠醢，主人辭以窶。濡肉齒決，乾肉不齒決。毋嘬炙。卒食，客自前跪，徹飯齊以授相者，主人興辭於客，然後客坐。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 49, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 49", "sort_key": "0049", "text_original": "侍飲於長者，酒進則起，拜受於尊所。長者辭，少者反席而飲。長者舉未釂，少者不敢飲。", "text_normalized": "侍飲於長者，酒進則起，拜受於尊所。長者辭，少者反席而飲。長者舉未釂，少者不敢飲。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 50, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 50", "sort_key": "0050", "text_original": "長者賜，少者、賤者不敢辭。賜果於君前，其有核者懷其核。御食於君，君賜餘，器之溉者不寫，其餘皆寫。", "text_normalized": "長者賜，少者、賤者不敢辭。賜果於君前，其有核者懷其核。御食於君，君賜餘，器之溉者不寫，其餘皆寫。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 51, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 51", "sort_key": "0051", "text_original": "餕餘不祭。父不祭子，夫不祭妻。", "text_normalized": "餕餘不祭。父不祭子，夫不祭妻。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 52, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 52", "sort_key": "0052", "text_original": "御同於長者，雖貳不辭，偶坐不辭。", "text_normalized": "御同於長者，雖貳不辭，偶坐不辭。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 53, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 53", "sort_key": "0053", "text_original": "羹之有菜者用梜，其無菜者不用梜。", "text_normalized": "羹之有菜者用梜，其無菜者不用梜。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 54, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 54", "sort_key": "0054", "text_original": "為天子削瓜者副之，巾以絺。為國君者華之，巾以綌。為大夫累之，士疐之，庶人齕之。", "text_normalized": "為天子削瓜者副之，巾以絺。為國君者華之，巾以綌。為大夫累之，士疐之，庶人齕之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 55, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 55", "sort_key": "0055", "text_original": "父母有疾，冠者不櫛，行不翔，言不惰，琴瑟不御，食肉不至變味，飲酒不至變貌，笑不至矧，怒不至詈。疾止復故。", "text_normalized": "父母有疾，冠者不櫛，行不翔，言不惰，琴瑟不御，食肉不至變味，飲酒不至變貌，笑不至矧，怒不至詈。疾止復故。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 56, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 56", "sort_key": "0056", "text_original": "有憂者側席而坐，有喪者專席而坐。", "text_normalized": "有憂者側席而坐，有喪者專席而坐。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 57, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 57", "sort_key": "0057", "text_original": "水潦降，不獻魚鱉，獻鳥者拂其首，畜鳥者則勿拂也。獻車馬者執策綏，獻甲者執胄，獻杖者執末。獻民虜者操右袂。獻粟者執右契，獻米者操量鼓。獻孰食者操醬齊。獻田宅者操書致。", "text_normalized": "水潦降，不獻魚鱉，獻鳥者拂其首，畜鳥者則勿拂也。獻車馬者執策綏，獻甲者執胄，獻杖者執末。獻民虜者操右袂。獻粟者執右契，獻米者操量鼓。獻孰食者操醬齊。獻田宅者操書致。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 58, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 58", "sort_key": "0058", "text_original": "凡遺人弓者：張弓尚筋，弛弓尚角。右手執簫，左手承弣。尊卑垂帨。若主人拜，則客還辟，辟拜。主人自受，由客之左接下承弣；鄉與客并，然後受。", "text_normalized": "凡遺人弓者：張弓尚筋，弛弓尚角。右手執簫，左手承弣。尊卑垂帨。若主人拜，則客還辟，辟拜。主人自受，由客之左接下承弣；鄉與客并，然後受。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 59, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 59", "sort_key": "0059", "text_original": "進劍者左首。進戈者前其鐏，後其刃。進矛戟者前其鐓。進几杖者拂之。效馬效羊者右牽之；效犬者左牽之。執禽者左首。飾羔雁者以繢。受珠玉者以掬。受弓劍者以袂。飲玉爵者弗揮。凡以弓劍、苞苴、簞笥問人者，操以受命，如使之容。", "text_normalized": "進劍者左首。進戈者前其鐏，後其刃。進矛戟者前其鐓。進几杖者拂之。效馬效羊者右牽之；效犬者左牽之。執禽者左首。飾羔雁者以繢。受珠玉者以掬。受弓劍者以袂。飲玉爵者弗揮。凡以弓劍、苞苴、簞笥問人者，操以受命，如使之容。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 60, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 60", "sort_key": "0060", "text_original": "凡為君使者，已受命，君言不宿於家。君言至，則主人出拜君言之辱；使者歸，則必拜送于門外。若使人於君所，則必朝服而命之；使者反，則必下堂而受命。", "text_normalized": "凡為君使者，已受命，君言不宿於家。君言至，則主人出拜君言之辱；使者歸，則必拜送于門外。若使人於君所，則必朝服而命之；使者反，則必下堂而受命。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 61, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 61", "sort_key": "0061", "text_original": "博聞強識而讓，敦善行而不怠，謂之君子。君子不盡人之歡，不竭人之忠，以全交也。", "text_normalized": "博聞強識而讓，敦善行而不怠，謂之君子。君子不盡人之歡，不竭人之忠，以全交也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 62, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 62", "sort_key": "0062", "text_original": "《禮》曰：「君子抱孫不抱子。」此言孫可以為王父尸，子不可以為父尸。為君尸者，大夫士見之，則下之。君知所以為尸者，則自下之，尸必式。乘必以几。", "text_normalized": "《禮》曰：「君子抱孫不抱子。」此言孫可以為王父尸，子不可以為父尸。為君尸者，大夫士見之，則下之。君知所以為尸者，則自下之，尸必式。乘必以几。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 63, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 63", "sort_key": "0063", "text_original": "齊者不樂不吊。", "text_normalized": "齊者不樂不吊。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 64, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 64", "sort_key": "0064", "text_original": "居喪之禮，毀瘠不形，視聽不衰。升降不由阼階，出入不當門隧。居喪之禮，頭有創則沐，身有瘍則浴，有疾則飲酒食肉，疾止復初。不勝喪，乃比於不慈不孝。五十不致毀，六十不毀，七十唯衰麻在身，飲酒食肉，處於內。", "text_normalized": "居喪之禮，毀瘠不形，視聽不衰。升降不由阼階，出入不當門隧。居喪之禮，頭有創則沐，身有瘍則浴，有疾則飲酒食肉，疾止復初。不勝喪，乃比於不慈不孝。五十不致毀，六十不毀，七十唯衰麻在身，飲酒食肉，處於內。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 65, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 65", "sort_key": "0065", "text_original": "生與來日，死與往日。知生者吊，知死者傷。知生而不知死，吊而不傷；知死而不知生，傷而不吊。", "text_normalized": "生與來日，死與往日。知生者吊，知死者傷。知生而不知死，吊而不傷；知死而不知生，傷而不吊。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 66, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 66", "sort_key": "0066", "text_original": "吊喪弗能賻，不問其所費。問疾弗能遺，不問其所欲。見人弗能館，不問其所舍。賜人者不曰來取。與人者不問其所欲。", "text_normalized": "吊喪弗能賻，不問其所費。問疾弗能遺，不問其所欲。見人弗能館，不問其所舍。賜人者不曰來取。與人者不問其所欲。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 67, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 67", "sort_key": "0067", "text_original": "適墓不登壟，助葬必執紼。臨喪不笑。揖人必違其位。望柩不歌。入臨不翔。當食不嘆。鄰有喪，舂不相。里有殯，不巷歌。適墓不歌。哭日不歌。送喪不由徑，送葬不辟涂潦。臨喪則必有哀色，執紼不笑，臨樂不嘆；介胄，則有不可犯之色。故君子戒慎，不失色於人。", "text_normalized": "適墓不登壟，助葬必執紼。臨喪不笑。揖人必違其位。望柩不歌。入臨不翔。當食不嘆。鄰有喪，舂不相。里有殯，不巷歌。適墓不歌。哭日不歌。送喪不由徑，送葬不辟涂潦。臨喪則必有哀色，執紼不笑，臨樂不嘆；介胄，則有不可犯之色。故君子戒慎，不失色於人。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 68, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 68", "sort_key": "0068", "text_original": "國君撫式，大夫下之。大夫撫式，士下之。禮不下庶人，刑不上大夫。刑人不在君側。", "text_normalized": "國君撫式，大夫下之。大夫撫式，士下之。禮不下庶人，刑不上大夫。刑人不在君側。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 69, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 69", "sort_key": "0069", "text_original": "兵車不式。武車綏旌，德車結旌。史載筆，士載言。前有水，則載青旌。前有塵埃，則載鳴鳶。前有車騎，則載飛鴻。前有士師，則載虎皮。前有摯獸，則載貔貅。行：前朱鳥而後玄武，左青龍而右白虎。招搖在上，急繕其怒。進退有度，左右有局，各司其局。", "text_normalized": "兵車不式。武車綏旌，德車結旌。史載筆，士載言。前有水，則載青旌。前有塵埃，則載鳴鳶。前有車騎，則載飛鴻。前有士師，則載虎皮。前有摯獸，則載貔貅。行：前朱鳥而後玄武，左青龍而右白虎。招搖在上，急繕其怒。進退有度，左右有局，各司其局。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 70, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 70", "sort_key": "0070", "text_original": "父之讎，弗與共戴天。兄弟之讎不反兵。交游之讎不同國。", "text_normalized": "父之讎，弗與共戴天。兄弟之讎不反兵。交游之讎不同國。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 71, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 71", "sort_key": "0071", "text_original": "四郊多壘，此卿大夫之辱也。地廣大，荒而不治，此亦士之辱也。", "text_normalized": "四郊多壘，此卿大夫之辱也。地廣大，荒而不治，此亦士之辱也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 72, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 72", "sort_key": "0072", "text_original": "臨祭不惰。祭服敝則焚之，祭器敝則埋之，龜策敝則埋之，牲死則埋之。凡祭於公者，必自徹其俎。", "text_normalized": "臨祭不惰。祭服敝則焚之，祭器敝則埋之，龜策敝則埋之，牲死則埋之。凡祭於公者，必自徹其俎。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 73, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 73", "sort_key": "0073", "text_original": "卒哭乃諱。禮，不諱嫌名。二名不偏諱。逮事父母，則諱王父母；不逮事父母，則不諱王父母。君所無私諱，大夫之所有公諱。《詩》、《書》不諱，臨文不諱。廟中不諱。夫人之諱，雖質君之前，臣不諱也；婦諱不出門。大功小功不諱。入竟而問禁，入國而問俗，入門而問諱。", "text_normalized": "卒哭乃諱。禮，不諱嫌名。二名不偏諱。逮事父母，則諱王父母；不逮事父母，則不諱王父母。君所無私諱，大夫之所有公諱。《詩》、《書》不諱，臨文不諱。廟中不諱。夫人之諱，雖質君之前，臣不諱也；婦諱不出門。大功小功不諱。入竟而問禁，入國而問俗，入門而問諱。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0074", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 74, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 74", "sort_key": "0074", "text_original": "外事以剛日，內事以柔日。凡卜筮日：旬之外曰遠某日，旬之內曰近某日。喪事先遠日，吉事先近日。曰：「為日，假爾泰龜有常，假爾泰筮有常。」卜筮不過三，卜筮不相襲。龜為卜，策為筮，卜筮者，先聖王之所以使民信時日、敬鬼神、畏法令也；所以使民決嫌疑、定猶與也。故曰：「疑而筮之，則弗非也；日而行事，則必踐之。」", "text_normalized": "外事以剛日，內事以柔日。凡卜筮日：旬之外曰遠某日，旬之內曰近某日。喪事先遠日，吉事先近日。曰：「為日，假爾泰龜有常，假爾泰筮有常。」卜筮不過三，卜筮不相襲。龜為卜，策為筮，卜筮者，先聖王之所以使民信時日、敬鬼神、畏法令也；所以使民決嫌疑、定猶與也。故曰：「疑而筮之，則弗非也；日而行事，則必踐之。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 75, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 75", "sort_key": "0075", "text_original": "君車將駕，則仆執策立於馬前。已駕，仆展軨、效駕，奮衣由右上取貳綏，跪乘，執策分轡，驅之五步而立。君出就車，則仆并轡授綏。左右攘辟，車驅而騶。至于大門，君撫仆之手而顧，命車右就車；門閭溝渠，必步。", "text_normalized": "君車將駕，則仆執策立於馬前。已駕，仆展軨、效駕，奮衣由右上取貳綏，跪乘，執策分轡，驅之五步而立。君出就車，則仆并轡授綏。左右攘辟，車驅而騶。至于大門，君撫仆之手而顧，命車右就車；門閭溝渠，必步。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 76, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 76", "sort_key": "0076", "text_original": "凡仆人之禮，必授人綏。若仆者降等，則受；不然，則否。若仆者降等，則撫仆之手；不然，則自下拘之。客車不入大門。婦人不立乘。犬馬不上於堂。", "text_normalized": "凡仆人之禮，必授人綏。若仆者降等，則受；不然，則否。若仆者降等，則撫仆之手；不然，則自下拘之。客車不入大門。婦人不立乘。犬馬不上於堂。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 77, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 77", "sort_key": "0077", "text_original": "故君子式黃髮，下卿位，入國不馳，入里必式。君命召，雖賤人，大夫士必自御之。介者不拜，為其拜而蓌拜。祥車曠左，乘君之乘車不敢曠左；左必式。仆御、婦人則進左手，後右手；御國君，則進右手、後左手而俯。", "text_normalized": "故君子式黃髮，下卿位，入國不馳，入里必式。君命召，雖賤人，大夫士必自御之。介者不拜，為其拜而蓌拜。祥車曠左，乘君之乘車不敢曠左；左必式。仆御、婦人則進左手，後右手；御國君，則進右手、後左手而俯。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1", "source_id": "liji-001-summary-of-the-rules-of-propriety-part-1__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 78, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曲禮上》 78", "sort_key": "0078", "text_original": "國君不乘奇車。車上不廣咳，不妄指。立視五巂，式視馬尾，顧不過轂。國中以策彗恤勿驅。塵不出軌。國君下齊牛，式宗廟。大夫士下公門，式路馬。乘路馬，必朝服載鞭策，不敢授綏，左必式。步路馬，必中道。以足蹙路馬芻，有誅。齒路馬，有誅。", "text_normalized": "國君不乘奇車。車上不廣咳，不妄指。立視五巂，式視馬尾，顧不過轂。國中以策彗恤勿驅。塵不出軌。國君下齊牛，式宗廟。大夫士下公門，式路馬。乘路馬，必朝服載鞭策，不敢授綏，左必式。步路馬，必中道。以足蹙路馬芻，有誅。齒路馬，有誅。", "notes": ""}
